Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.08,0:00:02.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:04.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:07.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你又在和人類玩耍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:10.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人類都很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:11.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我很喜歡他們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:12.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:17.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們也是時候考慮和他們共存了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:20.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不好  人類襲擊了我們龍族的村莊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:24.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們稍微安分點就立刻得寸進尺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.29,0:00:28.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人類  我決不饒恕你們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,爸爸媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:32.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:35.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不能再和人類玩耍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:36.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:40.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是人類殺害了你的雙親啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:43.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人類是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:46.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們不可能相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:23.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:25.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大家都睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:29.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒想到除了爸爸以外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:31.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看到的第一個傢伙會是自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:37.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:41.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是  很晚回家的話  提前說一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:43.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:45.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你臉紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:50.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:57.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼我會對這樣的托爾心動不已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:03:01.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,難不成我對托爾發情了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,總之你先穿上衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:04.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:08.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只要你變成了男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:13.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,會立刻暴露本性的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,讓我見識一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:17.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人類有多膚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:19.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她一定在想這些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:23.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,應該是伊露露用魔法將我變成了男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:26.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,如果能隨著時間流逝恢復就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然不知道伊露露對我有什麼企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:37.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但我只要保持平常心就行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:49.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小康娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:54.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,早上好  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:55.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:57.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為我覺得早上很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:02.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:10.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,現在這樣真不知道會發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,必須和大家保持距離
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,能不能讓托爾幫我變回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林變成雄性了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那事不宜遲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:21.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來做繁衍種族的行為吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:23.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:26.82,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(972,65)}乘上獨木舟去冒險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.66,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(972,65)}電視機前的大家也一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,教育節目
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.51,0:04:28.87,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,註：此處捏他自NHK播放的一檔教育節目《シャキーン》。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:32.91,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:34.87,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,快劃快划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:39.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:43.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有瀑布  大家抱緊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:49.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明這種事  女生之間做很正常的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:50.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我能忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:54.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不能被那些不知所謂的本能所支配
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:56.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,別纏著我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,別纏著我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:02.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:05.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以我說了  別隨便抱過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:06.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:07.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:17.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她以前跟我有這麼多肢體接觸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:23.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,太好了  變小了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:27.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,果然伊露露因為和托爾的戰鬥而變弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:33.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在托爾的世界中她所屬的勢力…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是叫混沌勢力來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:39.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,他們憎恨人類  並如此教育自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:43.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露就在這種環境中成長並且活到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就變成了現在的心境
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:53.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜已經睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:58.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要來晚酌一兩杯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:05.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:08.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,現在就先不要想這麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:14.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,之前好像也有過這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:15.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是春藥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:20.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我剛才就察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:24.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林現在是帶把兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:27.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是被伊露露施法了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可憐的小林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就由托爾來為你治好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾必須抓住機會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:39.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在心靈相通之後  就該是身體交融了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:42.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來吧  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一切都交給托爾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼你突然好萎靡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:49.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你竟然把女僕裝脫掉  不帶這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾  我要以男性的視角
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,把女僕的優點從頭到尾給你講清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:00.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:07.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已經撐過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下一步你準備怎麼辦呢  伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:21.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小姐  裝飾得真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:25.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,總感覺有哪裡不對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:28.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣就對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:30.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,原來如此
