Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.97,Kamisama S2 - Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur10\pos(988.8,594.8)}帥哥小林！（各種意義上）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:45.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,站住  不准逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你咋這麼能追  調和勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:54.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是屠龍派的克萊梅內
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:56.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,當你死的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在冥界的審判記得報上我的這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好讓我立功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:04.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:08.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露總是在我獨自一人的時候出現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:11.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就這麼等著能見到她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:17.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我好像對伊露露很執著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:20.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是因為覺得可以跟她交好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:27.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,至今為止遇到的異界人都很友好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:32.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明像是經歷了無數紛爭及其所導致的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是卻還願意接觸人類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是因為她們認為世界不只有這些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:42.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一定有戰爭以外的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我相信著這樣的托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:50.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以我才想要和伊露露和解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:54.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露沒有出現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:59.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒準她在路人少的這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:06.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,被看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:14.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這個世界的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:18.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我為屠戮這隻異世界的害獸而來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:21.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,速速離開此處
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:24.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,離開這裡並就此忘卻此事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:27.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這傢伙是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是來殺伊露露的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明是大人卻要殺一個小孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:32.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:35.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她是混沌派
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是只會給人類帶來災害的邪龍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:40.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:48.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:50.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這噪音令人如此不悅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:51.73,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,防狼警報器  助我一臂之力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:01.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,重死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,居然讓她逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:06.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼人類會救她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,外傷好像很快就癒合了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:21.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你為什麼要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,現在還不能說得救了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:27.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那傢伙一定會追過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:28.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,如果我在戰鬥中輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:34.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那也是我的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那麼被我救下來了  也算是你的命運吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:43.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:46.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是想向我宣洩什麼情緒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我在與你的交流中隱約察覺到這點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:54.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我不認可跟人類共存的龍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,龍不可能跟人類和諧共處的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:10:59.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你之前就說過這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為如果可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:06.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我至今為止的人生就為何…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:12.44,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,身為高等存在的龍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.32,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,與人類交好簡直是恥辱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:15.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,其實我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.86,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,發生了這麼多起悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:19.70,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,和解是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:20.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,其實我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:22.53,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,人類是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:23.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,想要繼續…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:24.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,繼續…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:38.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,想要繼續一起玩耍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:43.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然而誰都不允許我這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:46.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明那兩個孩子什麼錯都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:52.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:59.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那下次我們一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:04.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們一起經歷過了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:08.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,玩躲避球  逛漫展  去泡溫泉等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:13.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然並不亞於戰鬥的嬉戲還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:16.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你騙我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:19.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只是想說些漂亮話來哄騙我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:20.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:24.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我正試圖用些花言巧語
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:27.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來馴化你這頭兇惡且混沌的邪龍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:30.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你要選擇相信過往的教誨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:32.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還是選擇被我欺騙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:49.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒想到人類也是一伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:52.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你也要清除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:53.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:55.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你們不是有規矩的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,規矩早就形同虛設了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,而且這是龍與龍之間的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不適用於人類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:08.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,如此對比  托爾她爸爸還真是仁慈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:09.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,別太小瞧人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:17.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,居然還有企圖保護龍的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:22.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:26.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.69,0:13:31.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,超痛的  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:34.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來得太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:54.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你居然敢對小林動手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:56.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就算有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:58.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我叫援軍來也能解決
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我這就叫艾爾瑪大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你要是好好求饒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:08.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我就只毀你肉身  放過你的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:11.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來  求饒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:23.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你殺掉他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒有  我只是消除了有關這個世界的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然後扔回原來的世界去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:30.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,稍微教訓下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:31.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&HE0CDB7&\pos(427.2,240.6)}角
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:34.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:36.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣伊露露也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:40.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,放下心來以後  怎麼感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:44.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,龍的唾液有止血功效
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你只是想舔小林吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:51.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來吧小林  讓我舔舔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:55.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你這舌頭也太長了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,身為一名上班族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:04.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就要一味地認真執行規定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:07.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,公司優先於個人生活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我曾經是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:16.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為我總被教導自己有義務盡全力去完成工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:18.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等我回過神來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:21.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,私交的朋友都已不在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,而在此時  我邂逅了托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:27.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,自己才發生了改變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:30.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以  伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:34.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可能是把你看成從前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:40.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:41.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:42.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小康娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:46.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是我家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對  傷口也已經癒合了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:51.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:02.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼扯都拉不開她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:06.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這麼晚才察覺到小林的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:07.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我能被你欺騙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:15.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:29.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:33.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天由我厄爾尼諾·三木播報全國的天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,爪子還有尾巴等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:37.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不收起來沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.97,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,今日的大部分地區都是晴空萬里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還有胸也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:41.07,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,因為處於高氣壓的影響下將會出現大範圍的晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:41.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在日常生活很不方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:44.19,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,所以可以放心地曬衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,別看伊露露這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:45.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她保持現在這個身形已經是很勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:47.11,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,同時也到了櫻花的花季
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:47.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要是不勉強自己的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那對胸會更大的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但爪子和尾巴應該能隨時收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:55.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那為什麼惟獨胸部不能收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,分個至少5%給我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:50.99,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,因為處於開花初期所以這個時期還沒有這麼多蚊蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:56.41,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,那麼趁機今天去賞櫻也是個不錯的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.16,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,早上可能會有點冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:01.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:03.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是在這裡排尿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:07.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,得從這裡開始教啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:09.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對  坐在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:10.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:12.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:15.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看來還有很多東西得教啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:20.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要是這時候有個優秀的女僕就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我會對她刮目相看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:26.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:28.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只要在我工作的時候照顧她就行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:30.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:33.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我和小林要白頭偕老的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:36.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,別若無其事地說什麼白頭偕老
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:37.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:41.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你的肌肉有在鍛鍊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:42.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.62,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,肌肉不加鍛鍊就會減少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:44.79,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,會促進機體衰老…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:47.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她可是不久前還在相互廝殺的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:51.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾絕對不會原諒背叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:53.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要被肅清了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:56.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是我還想了解小林更多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:57.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可沒這麼容易被打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:17:59.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不准打架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:03.56,Kaboyoshi S2 - Webpage,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\b0\c&H4C4D48&\frz45.26\pos(918.666,542)}如何與人類生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:03.56,Kaboyoshi S2 - Webpage,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\b0\c&H4C4D48&\frz47.33\pos(1216,743.333)}小林托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:03.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:07.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是我寫的如何作為一個人類生活的指南手冊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,先把爪子變成人類的手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,笑這麼邪惡幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你連手都不會變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:29.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我變不好  就這樣用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這雙手能抓住東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:33.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像上面長有很多小手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:34.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:38.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:41.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人類通過「打招呼」來交流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:45.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,總之記住重複對方向你打招呼說過的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:46.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:49.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人類基本什麼都吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:52.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但不喜歡吃龍肉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:54.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,正在尋找可以讓人類吃下龍肉的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:56.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:57.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,想做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這內容的主觀性太強了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這可是我心中的真實想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:06.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,衣服要儘量穿得和人類一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:07.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣才不會很顯眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:10.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你穿的跟普通人有些不太一樣啊
Comment: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/The  異類
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:12.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:16.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也穿個適合人類穿的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:17.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這裡沒有適合你的尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不是有康娜的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:20.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以說尺寸不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:22.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你看  有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:26.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是不聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:29.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,跟我一樣  用鱗片變成衣服如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:32.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我做不到這麼巧妙的本領
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:35.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就借我的衣服來穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:38.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你接下來打算幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:40.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:41.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是想你做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒什麼想做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想做的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:48.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,讓我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:49.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:53.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在想好之前  可以在這個家裡待到你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:55.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,趕緊滾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:56.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,客套話都沒說全呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:19:59.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可能你會覺得意外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:02.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但我十分不情願讓你留在這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:04.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一點都不意外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:07.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為你想想  自己是以什麼形象出場的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:09.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,彷彿是個嗜血的狂戰士哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:13.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是因為和托爾戰鬥很有趣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:14.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不對  我當時是這種表情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:18.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,請快點找到你想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:21.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,正所謂「不勞者不得食」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:22.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那康娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜在做一份名為「小學生」的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:28.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我也做那份叫「小學生」的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:31.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,必須得是小孩才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你和我同齡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:35.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,盡情苦惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:43.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:45.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,說是在思考想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:55.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但願能找到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:20:59.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:01.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我找到自己總之想做的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:03.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想和小林造小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想了下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我已經到養兒育女的年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:14.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我缺少家人所產生的寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:16.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,想要讓小林來填滿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:18.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林和我造小孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:20.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:21.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這可不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,萬萬不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:24.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,而且我是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我再給你裝上就行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:28.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不行  要造也是和我造
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:30.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下流
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:31.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.06,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:35.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然我的貞操沒人要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:36.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但也絕不會給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:44.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是伊露露的
Comment: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:51.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,---ED---
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:22.46,Kobayashi S2 - Next,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\pos(961.333,664.667)}下回預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:24.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露睡哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:26.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒法再塞多張床了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:27.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這裡怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:28.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,壁櫥？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:29.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,讓人安心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.39,0:23:30.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露覺得好就行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.64,0:23:32.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我很中意
Comment: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:34.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/第三話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:34.97,Kobayashi S2 - Next,,0,0,0,,{\pos(949.333,728.667)\fad(300,0)}課外活動（當然不一般）
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.98,0:23:38.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,本週墮落的是誰呢
Dialogue: 1,0:23:38.75,0:23:39.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,巨蟹座
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.98,Kobayashi S2 - Screen 2,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(879.999,684.667)}可能會被捲入意外事件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.98,Kobayashi S2 - Screen 2,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(778.667,732.667)}幸運建議
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.98,Kobayashi S2 - Screen 2,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(798.666,871.334)}本來星座這玩意就毫無意義哦
